268
00:13:14,461 --> 00:13:16,761
GIVE IT A REST, CANDACE!

269
00:13:25,971 --> 00:13:27,739
YES! HEY, FERB!

270
00:13:27,741 --> 00:13:29,407
IT'S CANDACE'S BIRTHDAY.

271
00:13:29,409 --> 00:13:32,076
WE'VE GOTTA DO BETTER
THAN LAST YEAR.

272
00:13:32,078 --> 00:13:34,512
